WEBVTT

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:09.319
Stop bothering me.

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:14.080
Did you bring any soap?

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.519
- No.
- Nice game out there.

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:18.559
Hurry up.

00:00:18.559 --> 00:00:20.359
I know, I know.

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:05.609
- Hey Li Ming, what a coincidence.
- You're here.

00:01:05.609 --> 00:01:08.616
Looking good. Look at those muscles.

00:01:08.616 --> 00:01:11.535
I'm solid as a rock.

00:01:13.045 --> 00:01:14.624
Why is this part so soft?

00:01:14.624 --> 00:01:18.130
Get lost! Who cares about it being hard?

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:21.959
Chen Ke.

00:01:21.959 --> 00:01:24.670
I didn't realize you were so pale.

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:27.000
What are you doing?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.800
You pervert!

00:01:30.239 --> 00:01:31.319
What?

00:01:31.319 --> 00:01:34.360
You never shower with us,
but you'll shower with Chen Ke?

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:36.959
I... I'm just getting used to it.

00:01:36.959 --> 00:01:39.119
Used to what?

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:40.687
You're still wrapped in a towel?

00:01:40.687 --> 00:01:42.720
Just take it off already.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.280
It's just a shower.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:46.990
- Why go totally naked?
- Just take it off.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.959
Seriously.

00:01:48.959 --> 00:01:50.160
Look at you.

00:01:50.160 --> 00:01:51.960
I'm just kidding.

00:03:34.980 --> 00:03:37.990
[Episode 3: I kissed you because
I wanted to show my affection and blessings]

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:48.081
♪ I secretly cover your eyes ♪

00:03:48.081 --> 00:03:51.160
♪ And let you guess who I am ♪

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:53.440
Stop it.

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:56.000
I'm here for something serious.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:00.336
Lately, you and Chen Ke
have been joined at the hip.

00:04:00.336 --> 00:04:03.199
I thought you'd forgotten me.

00:04:03.199 --> 00:04:05.759
Now you finally remember me?

00:04:05.759 --> 00:04:07.359
It's all your fault.

00:04:07.359 --> 00:04:09.759
That crappy movie you showed on the trip...

00:04:09.759 --> 00:04:14.439
Now whenever I'm close to a guy,
it just feels weird.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.800
So you're blaming the movie?

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.840
Then let's just watch it again.

00:04:28.959 --> 00:04:31.120
Again?

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:33.360
You want me to suffer more?

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:34.719
Don't you get it?

00:04:34.719 --> 00:04:36.040
It's called exposure therapy.

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:39.159
Last time, you only saw the beginning,
and your mind started racing.

00:04:39.159 --> 00:04:40.825
Maybe once you finish it,

00:04:40.825 --> 00:04:44.399
you'll realize it's actually a beautiful,
tragic love story.

00:04:44.399 --> 00:04:48.120
Maybe then you won't be so restless.

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:50.280
Who's restless?

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:54.600
Play it.

00:05:03.786 --> 00:05:05.868
[The End - A movie by Wang Kar Wai]

00:05:10.839 --> 00:05:13.159
Why such a big reaction?

00:05:13.159 --> 00:05:14.959
You...

00:05:17.079 --> 00:05:19.480
Okay. The movie's over.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:21.400
How do you feel?

00:05:22.719 --> 00:05:26.840
If you don't feel anything, then...

00:05:27.480 --> 00:05:29.319
No.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.560
Nothing special.

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:33.680
That was sudden.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:38.680
What are you two doing
hiding in here with the curtains drawn?

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.399
I know.

00:05:42.399 --> 00:05:45.040
You're sneaking a peek at some porn.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:47.639
- Why didn't you invite me?
- Who's watching porn?

00:05:47.639 --> 00:05:49.639
That's all you think about.
Get your mind out of the gutter.

00:05:49.639 --> 00:05:53.040
Xiao Ming,
we just borrowed a Wong Kar Wai film.

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.921
Want to join us?

00:05:54.921 --> 00:05:56.480
Nah. Too artsy for me.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:58.120
I wouldn't get it.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:06:00.319
Showing him art is a total waste.

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:02.439
Like casting pearls before swine.

00:06:06.508 --> 00:06:08.095
[Chen Ke is calling]

00:06:10.519 --> 00:06:11.637
Where are you going, Yu Lei?

00:06:11.637 --> 00:06:14.057
Chen Ke asked me to practice baseball.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.334
Hey.

00:06:28.334 --> 00:06:30.880
I've got nothing else to do.
Let's play some games.

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:32.639
Do you know how to play Counter-Strike?

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:34.319
Who plays such violent games?

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:36.119
You're such a gorilla.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:38.920
Go on, get out of here.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:41.519
I think you should spend your time showering.

00:06:41.519 --> 00:06:43.000
You stink.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:44.576
Me?

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:50.560
Do I really smell that bad?

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:52.439
Stop being so picky.

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:06.880
Why do you keep smiling at me?

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:08.920
Is there something on my face?

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:09.920
It's nothing.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.839
I just figured something out.

00:07:11.839 --> 00:07:13.040
What?

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:14.920
Does it have to do with me?

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:17.920
Yu Lei, you're here to play too?

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:19.120
Welcome!

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:21.240
We're just here to watch.
Hope we're not interrupting practice.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:24.560
Not at all. Chen Ke, show Yu Lei the ropes.

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:28.040
We're always looking for
more people to join the club.

00:07:28.040 --> 00:07:30.213
- Thanks.
- No problem.

00:07:34.455 --> 00:07:36.920
What's going on?

00:07:36.920 --> 00:07:39.480
It's not like this in the anime "Touch".

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.199
It's okay. It's simple.

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:43.880
I'll show you.

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:45.680
Come here.

00:07:47.245 --> 00:07:50.560
October 15, 2001. Sunny.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.839
Today, Yu Lei seemed really happy.

00:07:53.839 --> 00:07:57.199
When I asked him why, he wouldn't say.

00:07:57.199 --> 00:08:01.120
But seeing him happy
makes me feel good too.

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:05.840
So, this is what having a close friend
feels like.

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:10.639
Want to try the stance I mentioned?

00:08:12.759 --> 00:08:14.639
What stance?

00:08:15.399 --> 00:08:18.319
The one from the book.

00:08:19.399 --> 00:08:22.000
You mean the traditional one?

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:24.120
So you like it old school?

00:08:24.120 --> 00:08:28.199
Is there really a difference?

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:31.800
Come on, one more time.

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:33.600
Okay.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:01.360
- Hand me that balloon.
- A bit higher.

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:02.639
- A little more to the left.
- Don't mess it up.

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:04.519
I got it, no problem.

00:09:04.519 --> 00:09:06.319
That's about right.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.266
Be careful.

00:09:10.266 --> 00:09:11.960
Time flies.

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:14.520
I can't believe Christmas is almost here.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:20.079
I remember when I was a kid,
it was my grandma's favorite holiday.

00:09:43.940 --> 00:09:47.589
But ever since she passed away,

00:09:47.589 --> 00:09:51.160
my family hasn't really celebrated it.

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:53.840
That's easy.

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.240
We can celebrate here at school this year.

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:58.439
It'll be fun.

00:09:58.439 --> 00:09:59.520
Forget it.

00:09:59.520 --> 00:10:01.679
It's right during final exams.

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:04.079
Everyone will be busy studying.

00:10:04.079 --> 00:10:06.359
Who's going to think about Christmas?

00:10:08.821 --> 00:10:11.391
[Victoria Italian Restaurant]

00:10:33.585 --> 00:10:37.036
[Christmas Plans with Chen Ke]

00:10:46.633 --> 00:10:49.100
[Chen Ke calling]

00:10:53.520 --> 00:10:55.880
December 20, 2001.

00:10:55.880 --> 00:10:57.479
Cloudy.

00:10:57.479 --> 00:11:01.839
Final exams are coming up,
but Yu Lei is busy with something.

00:11:01.839 --> 00:11:04.719
He's nowhere to be found
when I asked him to join me for revision.

00:11:04.719 --> 00:11:06.559
Aren't we friends?

00:11:06.559 --> 00:11:09.160
He didn't even say a word.

00:11:17.199 --> 00:11:18.647
Is this seat taken?

00:11:19.548 --> 00:11:21.548
No, go ahead.

00:11:36.319 --> 00:11:38.119
I'm heading out.

00:11:57.968 --> 00:11:59.768
Chen Ke.

00:12:01.160 --> 00:12:02.960
Hey, senior.

00:12:03.959 --> 00:12:05.400
Why are you eating alone?

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:06.719
Where's Yu Lei?

00:12:06.719 --> 00:12:08.799
Even I can't find him.

00:12:08.799 --> 00:12:10.559
I asked him to join me for revision today,

00:12:10.559 --> 00:12:12.040
but he didn't get back to me.

00:12:12.040 --> 00:12:14.319
He's probably busy with something.

00:12:14.319 --> 00:12:17.400
What's he being so secretive about?

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:19.519
Isn't he studying for the final exams?

00:12:21.304 --> 00:12:22.599
By the way,

00:12:22.599 --> 00:12:24.839
the school orchestra has a show on the 24th.

00:12:24.839 --> 00:12:26.520
I wanted to invite you guys.

00:12:26.520 --> 00:12:28.719
Since you're here,
I'll just give these to you.

00:12:28.719 --> 00:12:30.000
The 24th?

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:31.000
Yeah.

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:33.401
- We'll be in the middle of exams.
- I know.

00:12:33.401 --> 00:12:35.840
It's the last day of your exam week, right?

00:12:35.840 --> 00:12:38.799
Don't worry.
The performance is in the evening.

00:12:38.799 --> 00:12:41.280
It'll be a good way to relax.

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:44.399
Okay. Thanks, senior.

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:55.639
Yu Lei, what were you so busy with today?

00:12:56.559 --> 00:12:57.757
Me?

00:12:57.757 --> 00:13:00.640
I just went out to buy some things.

00:13:00.640 --> 00:13:04.399
- Why?
- Didn't you see my page?

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:09.040
I forgot to bring my pager today.

00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:10.079
Never mind.

00:13:10.079 --> 00:13:13.199
I wanted to ask you to study with me.

00:13:13.199 --> 00:13:15.439
I'm sorry. I...

00:13:15.439 --> 00:13:16.479
It's fine.

00:13:16.479 --> 00:13:18.920
Just don't disappear like that next time.

00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:22.224
- Got it.
- By the way, are you free on Christmas?

00:13:22.224 --> 00:13:23.574
Me?

00:13:24.400 --> 00:13:25.799
On Christmas?

00:13:25.799 --> 00:13:28.599
I might have some plans.

00:13:28.599 --> 00:13:30.399
What plans?

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.280
Don't worry about it.

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:34.800
Just some personal stuff.

00:13:37.479 --> 00:13:39.920
Hey man, you're back.

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:41.679
- Yeah.
- Exams are coming up.

00:13:41.679 --> 00:13:42.839
How's the studying going?

00:13:42.839 --> 00:13:44.880
Exams?

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:45.959
What exams?

00:13:45.959 --> 00:13:47.199
Are you serious?

00:13:47.199 --> 00:13:49.040
Final exams are next week.

00:13:49.040 --> 00:13:51.399
You really had no idea?

00:13:55.959 --> 00:13:58.400
Buddy, you have to help me.

00:13:58.400 --> 00:14:00.599
You've got to help me out!

00:14:41.520 --> 00:14:43.439
He Jin, give it a rest.

00:14:43.439 --> 00:14:45.640
Can you keep it down?

00:14:45.640 --> 00:14:46.719
Seriously.

00:14:46.719 --> 00:14:48.599
Go study in the hallway.

00:14:48.599 --> 00:14:50.840
Don't keep everyone awake.

00:14:54.799 --> 00:14:56.679
Just go to sleep.

00:14:56.679 --> 00:14:58.599
I have my own way of studying.

00:14:58.599 --> 00:15:00.759
We're all just trying to study.

00:15:03.199 --> 00:15:06.391
Battle, battle... protest, protest...

00:15:06.391 --> 00:15:09.400
Actually,
you don't need to memorize everything.

00:15:09.400 --> 00:15:12.599
Look at this chapter, and this one.

00:15:12.599 --> 00:15:14.719
The professor emphasized on these.

00:15:14.719 --> 00:15:16.999
I'm sure they'll be on the test.

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:21.400
It's okay.
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

00:15:21.400 --> 00:15:22.943
Thanks.

00:15:35.173 --> 00:15:37.305
Who needs your charity?

00:15:37.305 --> 00:15:39.649
[Focus on this topic]

00:15:42.839 --> 00:15:44.000
Alright, class.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.400
Ten minutes left.

00:15:46.400 --> 00:15:49.479
Please finish up your answers.

00:16:13.937 --> 00:16:16.671
[Heng Tai First High School]

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:31.040
"Zhang Han invited Yu Lei and me to a show."

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:32.609
"I'm heading there now.
Whoever gets back first,

00:16:32.609 --> 00:16:34.519
please let him know."

00:16:35.880 --> 00:16:37.680
What's this?

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:41.999
Looks fancy.

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:47.040
Chen Ke...

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:49.520
He Jin!

00:16:49.520 --> 00:16:51.559
Why are you using Chen Ke's skincare?

00:16:51.559 --> 00:16:53.439
I'm not, I'm just looking.

00:16:53.439 --> 00:16:55.079
Don't tell him.

00:16:55.079 --> 00:16:56.880
This brand is actually pretty good.

00:16:56.880 --> 00:16:58.799
If you want it, buy your own.

00:16:58.799 --> 00:17:01.120
Where's Chen Ke? I haven't seen him.

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.920
I think he's on a date.

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:05.599
- With who?
- How should I know?

00:17:31.439 --> 00:17:34.600
Xiao Ming, you're crazy!

00:17:34.600 --> 00:17:37.080
Yu Lei, he's lost it.

00:17:37.080 --> 00:17:38.801
- Just bear with it.
- Count yourself lucky.

00:17:38.801 --> 00:17:40.160
He already kissed the rest of us.

00:17:40.160 --> 00:17:42.239
You're the only one left.

00:17:45.360 --> 00:17:47.800
What? You guys aren't happy?

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:50.160
I'm showing my gratitude.

00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:52.039
Thanks to you, I'm sure I passed.

00:17:52.039 --> 00:17:54.039
No doubt about it.

00:17:55.239 --> 00:17:56.840
No way. I'm too happy.

00:17:56.840 --> 00:17:58.957
I have to kiss you again!

00:17:58.957 --> 00:18:01.436
- No, no, no!
- Stop it! Run!

00:18:02.999 --> 00:18:05.428
No one's getting away!

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:09.039
Give me some sugar!

00:18:09.039 --> 00:18:10.839
Help!

00:18:12.120 --> 00:18:13.920
Are you okay?

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:17.999
Buddy, I didn't mean it.

00:18:17.999 --> 00:18:19.288
Check if anything's broken.

00:18:19.288 --> 00:18:21.640
It's fine, don't worry about it.

00:18:21.640 --> 00:18:23.439
These are for you guys.

00:18:23.439 --> 00:18:25.439
Here, Xiao Ming.

00:18:25.439 --> 00:18:27.239
What's this? Let me see.

00:18:29.039 --> 00:18:30.199
It looks nice.

00:18:30.199 --> 00:18:31.519
- Here.
- Thanks.

00:18:31.519 --> 00:18:33.400
Yong.

00:18:33.400 --> 00:18:35.080
- Thanks, Yu Lei.
- Oh no.

00:18:35.080 --> 00:18:37.279
I was so focused on the exams,
I didn't get any gifts.

00:18:37.279 --> 00:18:38.719
- What should I do?
- It's okay.

00:18:38.719 --> 00:18:39.719
As long as you're happy.

00:18:39.719 --> 00:18:41.519
I don't care about that.

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:47.686
Guys, the three of us can
just each give him a kiss.

00:18:49.279 --> 00:18:50.800
Guys, that's really not necessary.

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:53.440
- Get him!
- Come here!

00:18:56.046 --> 00:18:57.967
I give up!

00:18:59.560 --> 00:19:01.920
Tell you what, let's go out and celebrate.

00:19:01.920 --> 00:19:04.039
Dinner, drinks, and karaoke.

00:19:04.039 --> 00:19:07.519
Whoever goes on a date is a loser.

00:19:07.519 --> 00:19:09.080
A total loser.

00:19:09.080 --> 00:19:10.960
Let's go.

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:16.475
Still pretending to study?

00:19:16.475 --> 00:19:18.120
- What are you talking about?
- Stop snatching.

00:19:18.120 --> 00:19:19.531
Let's come back here next time, okay?

00:19:19.531 --> 00:19:21.209
Sure.

00:19:22.679 --> 00:19:24.120
Come on, what are you looking at?

00:19:24.120 --> 00:19:27.759
Must be nice.
When will I ever get a girlfriend?

00:19:27.759 --> 00:19:28.800
You traitor.

00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:30.601
- Aren't we enough for you?
- Exactly.

00:19:30.601 --> 00:19:31.999
It's not the same.

00:19:31.999 --> 00:19:33.959
How is it different? Get him, Xiao Ming!

00:19:33.959 --> 00:19:35.080
So you're too good for us now?

00:19:35.080 --> 00:19:36.800
How dare you look down on us!

00:19:36.800 --> 00:19:38.720
Stop looking and hurry up.

00:19:47.918 --> 00:19:51.179
[School Orchestra Recital]

00:20:00.239 --> 00:20:01.600
- Not bad.
- Sounds great.

00:20:01.600 --> 00:20:03.400
Yeah.

00:20:24.920 --> 00:20:26.360
Dear Ke Ke,

00:20:26.360 --> 00:20:29.120
I bet you're wondering what I've been up to.

00:20:29.120 --> 00:20:30.735
Well, here's the answer.

00:20:30.735 --> 00:20:35.039
I was getting this Christmas gift ready,
and planning today's date.

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:39.719
I'm sorry for neglecting you
these past few days.

00:20:39.719 --> 00:20:42.400
But by now, we should have
already had a great dinner

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:44.039
and seen a movie.

00:20:44.039 --> 00:20:49.880
I hope when you see this gift,
you'll feel like it's been a perfect day.

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:55.079
Stop drinking.

00:20:59.320 --> 00:21:01.160
You can't handle it, so why try?

00:21:01.160 --> 00:21:02.960
Seriously.

00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:06.400
That jerk Li Ming.

00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:10.320
He said whoever goes on a date is a loser.

00:21:10.320 --> 00:21:12.719
Then he just ditches us halfway through.

00:21:12.719 --> 00:21:17.560
But he didn't say he was going on a date.

00:21:17.560 --> 00:21:19.199
Are you blind?

00:21:19.199 --> 00:21:23.519
Didn't you see the look on his face
when he answered that call?

00:21:24.207 --> 00:21:26.247
It was disgusting.

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.960
What's up?

00:21:32.439 --> 00:21:34.559
Someone's over there.

00:21:37.439 --> 00:21:39.720
I think it's Chen Ke.

00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:43.984
Looks like he's looking for you.

00:21:43.984 --> 00:21:46.423
We'll head up first.

00:21:47.160 --> 00:21:48.999
Be safe.

00:21:50.840 --> 00:21:54.200
Why didn't you put on a coat?

00:21:55.439 --> 00:21:57.037
I...

00:22:00.239 --> 00:22:03.519
What if you catch a cold?

00:22:03.519 --> 00:22:05.160
I just wanted to see you.

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:06.405
Thanks for the gift.

00:22:06.405 --> 00:22:09.136
I was in such a rush, I forgot my coat.

00:22:09.136 --> 00:22:11.479
I thought you were on
a date with my sister.

00:22:11.479 --> 00:22:13.160
Why would you think that?

00:22:13.160 --> 00:22:16.719
She gave me two tickets for the both of us.

00:22:16.719 --> 00:22:20.400
But lately, I thought you were
ignoring me on purpose.

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:23.479
So, I was upset and didn't tell you.

00:22:23.479 --> 00:22:25.959
But I left a note on your desk.

00:22:25.959 --> 00:22:27.640
A note?

00:22:27.640 --> 00:22:31.080
But I went to your dorm.

00:22:31.080 --> 00:22:32.640
I didn't see any note.

00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:34.960
And He Jin didn't say anything.

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:44.679
Chen Ke, I'm the one who should be sorry.

00:22:44.679 --> 00:22:47.320
I wanted to surprise you so much

00:22:47.320 --> 00:22:49.360
that I forgot to consider your feelings.

00:22:49.360 --> 00:22:52.439
In the end, the surprise turned into a scare.

00:22:52.439 --> 00:22:54.719
It almost became a huge mess.

00:22:54.719 --> 00:22:56.999
I... I'm at fault too.

00:22:56.999 --> 00:22:58.880
I should have just talked to you.

00:22:58.880 --> 00:23:00.479
With all these misunderstandings,

00:23:00.479 --> 00:23:02.839
we almost missed each other.

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:07.279
What's going on?

00:23:07.279 --> 00:23:09.600
Is this an apology convention?

00:23:09.600 --> 00:23:13.200
Yeah. At least we're together now.

00:23:15.999 --> 00:23:17.959
The shops are still open.

00:23:17.959 --> 00:23:20.519
Come on. Let's go celebrate.

00:23:32.560 --> 00:23:34.999
I almost forgot to give your coat back.

00:23:34.999 --> 00:23:37.120
Don't catch a cold in this weather.

00:23:37.120 --> 00:23:38.840
It's okay, I'm not cold.

00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:41.519
See? I'm still steaming.

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:46.800
Oh, right. I forgot to give you your gift.

00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:48.800
What is it?

00:23:48.800 --> 00:23:52.088
When I saw the scarf you gave me,

00:23:52.088 --> 00:23:54.471
I wasn't sure what to get you in return.

00:23:54.471 --> 00:23:55.791
So I bought this.

00:23:55.791 --> 00:23:57.097
It's a serum.

00:23:57.097 --> 00:23:59.640
I hope you like it.

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:03.640
I didn't know you were so bold, Chen Ke.

00:24:03.640 --> 00:24:05.880
Running out without a coat
just to buy me a gift?

00:24:05.880 --> 00:24:07.439
What are you talking about?

00:24:07.439 --> 00:24:11.279
I'm just missing a jacket,
not running around nude.

00:24:11.279 --> 00:24:14.640
Even if you were, I wouldn't mind.

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:16.239
Alright, stop it.

00:24:16.239 --> 00:24:17.920
Go on. Open it.

00:24:17.920 --> 00:24:19.576
Okay.

00:24:21.560 --> 00:24:23.360
Do you like it?

00:24:24.080 --> 00:24:27.319
You're so thoughtful, Ke Ke.

00:24:28.199 --> 00:24:30.519
It's fine. I'd love anything you give me.

00:24:30.519 --> 00:24:32.679
I'm going to take it out now.

00:24:32.679 --> 00:24:34.840
Go ahead.

00:24:34.840 --> 00:24:37.239
Come here. Follow me.

00:24:40.360 --> 00:24:42.400
Okay. I'm really taking it out.

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:45.640
- Merry Christmas. Ta-da!
- Merry Christmas. Ta-da!

00:24:45.640 --> 00:24:48.024
- I got one too?
- Me too!

00:24:48.024 --> 00:24:51.239
- I hope you like it.
- I'll love anything you give me.

00:24:51.239 --> 00:24:53.039
Keep it down. Don't let anyone hear us.

00:24:53.039 --> 00:24:54.920
Is it okay for us to be hiding here?

00:24:54.920 --> 00:24:56.479
Maybe we should go back to the dorm.

00:24:56.479 --> 00:24:57.519
It's fine.

00:24:57.519 --> 00:24:58.719
Look how happy they are.

00:24:58.719 --> 00:25:00.479
They won't notice us.

00:25:00.479 --> 00:25:02.719
Guess what it is.

00:25:02.719 --> 00:25:04.519
Something I'll love, for sure.

00:25:04.519 --> 00:25:06.679
Wow. I really do love it.

00:25:06.679 --> 00:25:08.600
See? I knew you would.

00:25:08.600 --> 00:25:10.320
Here. See if it looks good.

00:25:10.320 --> 00:25:11.824
Let's try it on.

00:25:13.360 --> 00:25:15.360
- Not bad.
- What do you think? Pretty good, right?

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:17.239
It's beautiful.

00:25:18.039 --> 00:25:20.079
So pretty.

00:25:20.800 --> 00:25:22.920
Here. Can you put some on me?

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:24.439
- Sure.
- Here.

00:25:24.439 --> 00:25:26.030
Hurry up.

00:25:27.920 --> 00:25:29.679
- Don't get it everywhere.
- I'll put some on too.

00:25:29.679 --> 00:25:31.320
It's smudging.

00:25:32.039 --> 00:25:33.562
What?

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:36.640
It's fine. Does it look good?

00:25:36.640 --> 00:25:38.120
Yeah.

00:25:38.120 --> 00:25:40.560
Why do you smell so good today?

00:25:40.560 --> 00:25:42.360
Let me smell.

00:25:42.999 --> 00:25:44.799
Come here.

00:25:46.387 --> 00:25:49.320
Oh, Rose! Are you going to jump?

00:25:49.320 --> 00:25:50.479
No! Don't do it!

00:25:50.479 --> 00:25:52.439
Give me your hand!

00:25:52.439 --> 00:25:55.039
Oh, Jack! Don't come any closer!

00:25:55.039 --> 00:25:56.800
Stay back!

00:25:56.800 --> 00:25:58.840
Oh, Rose...

00:25:58.840 --> 00:26:00.039
Don't jump!

00:26:00.039 --> 00:26:02.400
The snow down there is freezing.

00:26:02.400 --> 00:26:04.400
You'll definitely regret it.

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:05.959
I've made up my mind.

00:26:05.959 --> 00:26:08.199
I'm jumping right now!

00:26:08.199 --> 00:26:13.479
- Fine. You jump, I jump.
- Don't let anyone see us.

00:26:13.479 --> 00:26:16.279
There's no one here. One more kiss.

00:26:16.279 --> 00:26:18.160
Stop it.

00:26:21.999 --> 00:26:23.920
Hey! Get back to your dorms!

00:26:23.920 --> 00:26:25.720
Look at the time!

00:26:26.840 --> 00:26:27.920
Hurry, let's go.

00:26:27.920 --> 00:26:30.719
- Go, go.
- Let's go.

00:26:30.719 --> 00:26:31.719
Careful.

00:26:31.719 --> 00:26:33.439
Slow down, baby.

00:26:33.439 --> 00:26:35.479
It's so slippery.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:38.992
Hurry up.

00:26:39.920 --> 00:26:42.160
Carry my things.

00:26:42.160 --> 00:26:43.999
Watch your step.

00:26:44.937 --> 00:26:45.960
Let's go.

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:47.799
How did they...

00:26:53.600 --> 00:26:54.719
Lights out soon!

00:26:54.719 --> 00:26:55.840
Get back to your rooms!

00:26:55.840 --> 00:26:57.800
Or I'll mark your names down!

00:27:05.279 --> 00:27:09.039
How did we even squeeze into this tiny space?

00:27:09.800 --> 00:27:11.800
I have no idea.

00:27:11.800 --> 00:27:15.600
But now I know what it feels like
to run for your life.

00:27:15.600 --> 00:27:17.759
Hey, you two! Stop there!

00:27:17.759 --> 00:27:19.080
Stop chasing me!

00:27:19.080 --> 00:27:20.393
I'm not in a relationship!

00:27:20.393 --> 00:27:22.479
I told you we shouldn't have kissed.

00:27:52.840 --> 00:27:55.080
We aren't even a couple.

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:57.360
Why were we hiding?

00:27:57.360 --> 00:27:59.880
Then why did you kiss me?

00:27:59.880 --> 00:28:01.120
You scared me.

00:28:01.120 --> 00:28:02.279
I...

00:28:02.279 --> 00:28:04.759
It wasn't really a kiss.

00:28:05.519 --> 00:28:08.039
I just accidentally bumped into you.

00:28:08.039 --> 00:28:11.880
And then I thought...
you're actually a good kisser.

00:28:11.880 --> 00:28:14.439
Alright, that's enough.

00:28:14.439 --> 00:28:18.999
But foreigners kiss all the time
during holidays.

00:28:18.999 --> 00:28:21.920
Isn't it just a greeting?

00:28:21.920 --> 00:28:26.211
But if two people are really close,

00:28:26.211 --> 00:28:29.279
isn't it natural
to want to be physically close too?

00:28:29.279 --> 00:28:33.120
And if two people are physically close,

00:28:33.120 --> 00:28:37.039
doesn't that mean
they want to be close mentally?

00:28:37.039 --> 00:28:41.445
Look, handshakes, shoulder-grabs,
hugs, and kisses...

00:28:41.445 --> 00:28:45.439
they might look different,
but they're actually all the same.

00:28:45.439 --> 00:28:47.519
They all represent intimacy.

00:28:47.519 --> 00:28:50.880
Is intimacy only for couples?

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:56.360
Can't friends or family show it too?

00:28:56.360 --> 00:28:57.519
Is that how it works?

00:28:57.519 --> 00:28:59.080
Of course.

00:28:59.080 --> 00:29:04.600
I kissed you because I wanted to
show my affection and blessings.

00:29:04.600 --> 00:29:08.519
And you didn't push me away
because you accepted them.

00:29:08.519 --> 00:29:11.880
See? We're perfectly in sync.

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:13.279
Alright, Ke Ke.

00:29:13.279 --> 00:29:16.600
Merry Christmas.

00:29:20.467 --> 00:29:22.673
[Enjoy the winter holidays]

00:29:24.039 --> 00:29:27.880
This is the only time we have
before the break.

00:29:27.880 --> 00:29:29.959
It's not like we won't see each other again.

00:29:29.959 --> 00:29:32.239
We'll be back after the holidays.

00:29:32.239 --> 00:29:33.806
Yeah.

00:29:35.120 --> 00:29:36.199
Alright.

00:29:36.199 --> 00:29:38.360
I really have to go.

00:29:38.360 --> 00:29:39.880
Have a safe trip.

00:29:39.880 --> 00:29:41.680
Take care.

00:29:47.759 --> 00:29:50.360
Ke Ke! Wait!

00:29:50.360 --> 00:29:52.200
What now?

00:29:55.640 --> 00:29:59.360
I just realized I haven't
given you my home number.

00:30:00.199 --> 00:30:02.839
Here. Give me yours too.

00:30:03.959 --> 00:30:08.519
This feels like that long,
dramatic goodbye in "The Butterfly Lovers".

00:30:08.519 --> 00:30:12.640
So, which one of us is Liang Shan Bo
and which one is Zhu Ying Tai?

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:14.239
What are you talking about?

00:30:14.239 --> 00:30:16.320
That was a man and a woman.

00:30:16.320 --> 00:30:18.920
But we're both guys.

00:30:19.959 --> 00:30:23.999
I suspect Liang Shan Bo
wanted to be with Zhu Ying Tai

00:30:23.999 --> 00:30:26.479
even before he knew she was a girl.

00:30:29.239 --> 00:30:31.160
Alright. I'll stop teasing you.

00:30:31.160 --> 00:30:32.519
Go on.

00:30:32.519 --> 00:30:35.239
Happy New Year in advance.

00:30:36.600 --> 00:30:37.957
Bye.

00:30:43.120 --> 00:30:46.320
[Next Episode]
If you like it, I can teach you.

00:30:46.320 --> 00:30:48.320
I'll pass.

00:30:48.320 --> 00:30:49.800
Look at my hands.

00:30:49.800 --> 00:30:51.160
They're like bear paws.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:52.759
Your hands are cute.

00:30:52.759 --> 00:30:54.799
They don't look like bear paws.

00:31:02.959 --> 00:31:07.239
People who are close
probably do want to be more intimate.

00:31:07.239 --> 00:31:09.880
No wonder when he put that scarf on me,

00:31:09.880 --> 00:31:12.360
I had the sudden urge to kiss him.